    "body" : "<p>Another option is to use <em>relative indexing</em>: The format specifier references the same argument as the last format specifier.</p>\n\n<p>For example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String.format(\"%s %&lt;s %&lt;s %&lt;s\", \"hello\")\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>results in <code>hello hello hello hello</code>.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 8566752,
