    "answer_id" : 51269523,
    "question_id" : 6891175,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You need to use the index argument <code>%[argument_index$]</code> as the following:</p>\n<pre><code>String hello = &quot;Hello&quot;;\nString.format(&quot;%1$s %1$s %1$s %1$s %1$s %1$s&quot;, hello);\n</code></pre>\n<p>Result: <code>Hello Hello Hello Hello Hello Hello</code></p>\n"
  } ],
